

src/
├── Components/                // Reusable UI components
│   ├── Sidebar/               // Sidebar navigation
│   ├── TopBar/                // TopBar with user profile, notifications
│   ├── Widgets/               // Small data widgets for display
│   ├── Charts/                // Chart components (bar, pie, line)
│   ├── ProgressBars/          // Linear and Circular ProgressBars
│   ├── DataTable/             // Table component for tabular data
│   └── Forms/                 // User Management forms (add/edit user)
├── Pages/                     // Separate pages for dashboard sections
│   ├── Dashboard/             // Main dashboard page
│   ├── Users/                 // User management page
│   ├── Reports/               // Reports and insights page
│   └── Settings/              // App settings page
├── Contexts/                  // Context API for state management
│   └── DashboardContext.js    // Dashboard-wide global state
├── Services/                  // API calls (Axios/Fetch for backend data)
├── App.js                     // Main entry point with React Router
└── index.js                   // React application entry
